1%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENelson%20welded%20the%20two%20pipes%20together.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zack%20Nelson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20decided%20to%20bury%20the%20pipes%20about%20six%20feet%20underground%2C%20deep%20enough%20to%20protect%20from%20a%20catastrophe%20and%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20thermal%20insulation%20from%20the%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20accommodate%20the%20size%20of%20the%20pipes%2C%20he%20had%20to%20dig%20a%20hole%20over%2018%20feet%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENelson%20told%20BI%20excavating%20his%20property%20was%20by%20far%20the%20most%20dangerous%20part%20of%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20always%20the%20risk%20the%20hole%20could%20collapse%20into%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221136%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bunker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a988f943bb77284b9e4086%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22580%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENelson's%20project%20required%20a%20hole%20that%20was%20over%2018%20feet%20deep.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zack%20Nelson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENelson%20said%20he%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20how%20cheap%20it%20was%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20crane%2C%20which%20cost%20%241%2C864.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221266%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bunker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a98579dcdb354a9858ba32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22651%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENelson%20used%20cranes%20to%20deposit%20the%20pipes%20into%20the%20hole.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zack%20Nelson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20had%20to%20set%20up%20an%20entrance%20structure%20using%20steel%20and%20added%20space%20for%20an%20elevator%20shaft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221137%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bunker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a98d8643bb77284b9e42f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22582%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bunker%20also%20needed%20an%20entrance.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zack%20Nelson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20pipes%20and%20entrance%20had%20been%20set%20up%2C%20the%20next%20step%20was%20to%20fill%20the%20hole%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20a%20more%20difficult%20process%20than%20expected%20and%20involved%20a%20series%20of%20steps%20to%20ensure%20the%20dirt%20and%20gravel%20settled%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221146%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bunker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a98f2b43bb77284b9e4406%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20took%20several%20steps%20to%20fill%20the%20hole.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zack%20Nelson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20hole%20was%20filled%20in%20and%20he'd%20added%20sod%20to%20cover%20the%20freshly%20dug%20ground%2C%20the%20only%20identifier%20for%20the%20bunker%20was%20the%20entrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222860%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bunker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aa8d74dcdb354a9858e46c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221552%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENelson%20covered%20the%20ground%20in%20sod.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Zack%20Nelson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20said%20his%20goal%20was%20to%20get%20the%20bunker%20set%20up%20underground%20in%20time%20for%20winter.%20He%20still%20needs%20to%20structure%20the%20interior%20of%20the%20pipes%2C%20including%20an%20elevator%2C%20a%20primary%20bedroom%2C%20a%20bedroom%20with%20bunk%20beds%2C%20a%20kitchen%2C%20and%20a%20bathroom.%20Nelson%20also%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20%26quot%3Bman%20cave%26quot%3B%20area%20with%20a%20massive%20flatscreen%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20a%20dream%20of%20mine%20since%20I%20was%20a%20little%20kid%20to%20have%20an%20awesome%20hideout%20filled%20with%20technologies%20where%20a%20man%20can%20just%20chill%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said%20in%20his%20initial%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-inside-luxury-bunkers-ultra-rich-prepare-for-doomsday-2022-9%23vivos-told-insider-its-shelters-are-designed-to-allow-residents-to-operate-for-a-minimum-of-one-year-without-having-to-return-to-the-outside-world-it-said-its-customers-are-not-the-elite-1-but-rather-well-educated-average-people-with-a-keen-awareness-of-the-current-global-events-18%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebunker%20enthusiasts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nelson%20told%20BI%20he's%20not%20a%20prepper%20and%20that%20the%20project's%20main%20goal%20is%20to%20drum%20up%20additional%20funding%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnotawheelchair.com%2Fproducts%2Fthe-rig%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewheelchair%20manufacturing%20company%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Throughout%20the%20process%2C%20Nelson%20has%20sold%20jars%20of%20dirt%20from%20the%20excavation%20project%20and%20branded%20t-shirts%2C%20which%20he%20said%20has%20helped%20pay%20for%20the%20project%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20millions%20of%20views%20his%20videos%20have%20generated%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20keep%20enough%20water%20and%20food%20in%20the%20bunker%20so%20his%20family%20could%20survive%20underground%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20everyone%20at%20some%20point%20imagines%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20imminent%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%20Still%2C%20the%20bunker%20is%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20nice%20to%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-builds-underground-bunker-survival-prepper-less-than-100k-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705747621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a952e943bb77284b9e1e09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-builds-underground-bunker-survival-prepper-less-than-100k-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22YouTuber%20JerryRigEverything%20built%20his%20own%20bunker%20and%20documented%20the%20months-long%20process%20in%20a%20series%20of%20videos.%20Still%2C%20he%20says%20he's%20not%20a%20prepper.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gkay%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Kay)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-builds-underground-bunker-survival-prepper-less-than-100k-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%3A%20A%20Stage%20for%20the%20Visible%20Display%20of%20BJP's%20Extremely%20Backward%20Class%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20152337%2Fimage-1775.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20fortnight%2C%20the%20sight%20of%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Flucknow-news%2Flucknowayodhya-highway-s-tale-from-shadow-of-frenzy-to-sheen-of-pilgrims-progress-101705690948804.html%5C%22%3Ewalking%20along%20the%20road%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Lucknow%20to%20Ayodhya%20is%20a%20fair%20indication%20of%20the%20events%20that%20lie%20ahead%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20numbers%20are%20forcing%20the%20government%20to%20call%20a%20halt%20to%20those%20making%20the%20journey%20on%20foot.%20Devotees%2C%20some%20with%20their%20face%20painted%20to%20portray%20the%20Vanar%20sena%20of%20Rama%2C%20have%20been%20accompanying%20the%20religious%20paraphernalia%20headed%20to%20the%20temple%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterspersed%20among%20the%20sadhus%20and%20ascetics%20are%20a%20number%20of%20young%20men%2C%20many%20from%20the%20non-dominant%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20community%20or%20the%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBCs).%20In%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20supposedly%20new%20nation%20being%20unveiled%20on%20January%2022%2C%20their%20presence%20is%20significant%2C%20albeit%20a%20largely%20unremarked%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20main%20temple%20is%20dedicated%20to%20a%20Kshatriya%20King%2C%20there%20is%20a%20role%20for%20a%20supporting%20cast%2C%20such%20as%20the%20ancillary%20temple%20for%20Nishad%20Raj%20Guha%2C%20the%20king%20of%20the%20boatmen%2C%20who%20befriended%20Ram%20during%20his%20exile.%20Guha%20is%20now%20regarded%20as%20the%20progenitor%20of%20various%20riverine%20OBC%20communities%20collectively%20known%20as%20Nishad.%20This%20vision%20of%20Hinduism%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20challenge%20the%20Varna%20system%2C%20where%20the%20Shudra%20OBC%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20Tribals%20are%20meant%20to%20play%20a%20supporting%20role%20to%20%E2%80%98upper%20caste%E2%80%99%20heroes.%20However%2C%20it%20does%20provide%20space%20and%20recognition%20to%20several%20communities%20that%2C%20until%20that%20point%2C%20had%20received%20little%20political%20acknowledgment%20in%20independent%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENear%20Rudauli%2C%20about%2050%20kilometres%20from%20Faizabad%20town%2C%20we%20engage%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20Vikas%20Kumar%20Vishwakarma.%20He%20is%20one%20of%20eight%20men%20in%20their%20mid-30s%20taking%20a%20break%20for%20tea%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20reach%20Ayodhya%20%E2%80%9Cwell%20in%20time.%E2%80%9D%20Further%2C%20no%20further%20explanation%20is%20needed%2C%20not%20on%20this%20road%2C%20where%20every%20few%20metres%2C%20visual%20imagery%20in%20saffron%2C%20of%20all%20sorts%2C%20heralds%20January%2022%20almost%20as%20a%20day%20of%20Hindu%20reckoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20road%20to%20Ayodhya%20is%20feeling%20very%20important%20these%20days.%20That%20is%20how%20auspicious%20these%20times%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikas%2C%20as%20he%20reapplies%20a%20yellow%20paste%20on%20his%20forehead%2C%20which%20will%20then%20be%20inscribed%20with%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145109%2Fimage-1771.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221128%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145109%2Fimage-1771.png%201128w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145109%2Fimage-1771-300x186.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145109%2Fimage-1771-1024x635.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20road%20to%20Ayodhya.%20Photo%3A%20Ananta%20Jain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20member%20of%20the%20group%2C%20Rakesh%20Vishwakarma%2C%20interrupts%20to%20explain%20why%20he%20is%20going%20to%20Ayodhya.%20%E2%80%9CModi%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20said%20the%20day%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Pran%20Pratishta%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20will%20be%20a%20new%20Independence%20Day%20for%20Bharat.%20For%20our%20Vishwakarma%20community%2C%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20an%20even%20greater%20pride%20as%20we%20are%20the%20creators%20of%20the%20idol%20at%20the%20temple%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20acknowledges%20our%20community%20at%20every%20opportunity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%3Cem%3Esamman%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20respect%20carries%20a%20potent%20charge%20and%20this%20is%20the%20perception%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20combine%20is%20providing%20them.%20Hailing%20from%20the%20neighboring%20Barabanki%2C%20Rakesh%20recently%20joined%20this%20group%20just%20a%20few%20hours%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20saw%20my%20people%20marching%20towards%20Ayodhya%2C%20I%20left%20my%20work%20and%20decided%20to%20accompany%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parallel%20between%20January%2022%2C%20the%20consecration%20day%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20Independence%20Day%20was%20drawn%20not%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20as%20Rakesh%20believed%2C%20but%20by%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Trust.%20In%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fram-temple-in-ayodhya-jan-22-is-as-important-as-august-15-says-trust-chief-champat-rai%2Fvideoshow%2F106230355.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20Rai%C2%A0%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CJanuary%2022%2C%202024%2C%20is%20as%20important%20as%20August%2015%2C%201947.%20It%20is%20equally%20important%20as%20getting%20Kargil%20back%2C%20and%20as%20much%20as%20the%20detention%20of%20a%20lakh%20soldiers%20was%20important%20in%201971.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Findependence-on-january-22-the-noise-generated-around-it-bears-more-resemblance-to-force-a-divide%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Independence%E2%80%99%20on%20January%2022%3F%20The%20Noise%20Generated%20Is%20More%20Likely%20to%20Force%20a%20Divide%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Not%20about%20%3Cem%3Erajniti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20%3Cem%3Eaastha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20group%20of%20men%20from%20the%20Vishwakarma%20community%2C%20one%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20most%20backward%20castes%2C%20seemed%20to%20endorse%20the%20comparison.%20Vikas%2C%20aged%2028%2C%20is%20the%20youngest%20in%20the%20group.%20He%20disagreed%20with%20this%20perspective.%20However%2C%20he%20emphasised%20why%20this%20date%20has%20been%20put%20on%20a%20different%20pedestal.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20this%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20Independence%20Day.%20The%20Ram%20Mandir%20is%20not%20about%20%3Cem%3Erajniti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(politics)%2C%20it%20is%20about%20%3Cem%3Eaastha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(faith).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20has%20pursued%20a%20degree%20from%20a%20polytechnical%20institution%20and%20has%20been%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20without%20success.%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20his%20extended%20family%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20followed%20their%20caste%20occupation%20but%20were%20left%20with%20very%20little%20work%20during%20those%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20think%20we%20make%20statues%2C%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20romantic%20view.%20The%20staple%20of%20our%20work%20is%20masonry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20%3Cem%3Eaastha%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20taking%20you%20to%20Ayodhya%2C%20where%20does%20%3Cem%3Erajniti%3C%2Fem%3E%20take%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask.%20Without%20a%20pause%2C%20he%20says%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20BJP%20voter%20and%20then%20feels%20the%20need%20to%20explain%2C%20%E2%80%9CNarendra%20Modi%20has%20given%20our%20community%20%3Cem%3Esamman.%20%3C%2Fem%3EHe%20even%20invited%20a%20Vishwakarma%20to%20hoist%20a%20flag%20outside%20the%20new%20Parliament%20on%20his%20birthday.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20ask%20about%20tangible%20socio-economic%20benefits%2C%20whether%20the%20community%20has%20benefited%20from%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Vishwakarma%20Yojana%2C%20a%20scheme%20launched%20in%20September%202023%20aimed%20at%20supporting%20artisans%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20work%20with%20their%20hands%20and%20tools.%E2%80%9D%20The%20scheme%20covers%2018%20trades%2C%20including%20carpenters%2C%20blacksmiths%20and%20masons%2C%20all%20linked%20to%20caste%20occupations%20associated%20with%20the%20EBC%20and%20Dalit%20communities.%20However%2C%20most%20of%20the%20people%20in%20this%20group%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20and%20those%20who%20had%20said%20they%20had%20were%20unclear%20on%20what%20it%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20Ram%20Chandra%20Jangra%2C%20who%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20pushing%20the%20Vishwakarma%20Yojana%20from%20the%20BJP.%20He%20is%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Haryana.%20He%20agreed%20the%20scheme%20had%20not%20been%20properly%20implemented%20and%20its%20budget%20needed%20to%20be%20enhanced.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20the%20Vishwakarma%20community%20stands%20firmly%20with%20the%20BJP%20as%20the%20community%20always%20had%20strong%20Hindu%20ethos%2C%20and%20now%20the%20party%20has%20worked%20to%20bring%20them%20into%20their%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20convinced%20that%20even%20those%20Vishwakarma%20leaders%20who%20have%20gone%20to%20other%20parties%20would%20return%20to%20the%20BJP.%20He%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Modi%2C%20who%20has%20personally%20invited%20the%20Gujarat-based%20architect%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20Chandrakant%20Sompura%2C%20and%20his%20family%20for%20the%20Bhoomi%20Pujan.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20remember%20that%20Shah%20Jahan%20got%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20built%20or%20the%20Birlas%20got%20temples%20made%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20architects%20will%20be%20remembered%2C%20a%20family%20from%20our%20community.%20%3Cem%3ELog%20bhaavnaon%20se%20bhi%20nirmit%20hote%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(People%20are%20also%20constructed%20out%20of%20sentiment).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sompuras%2C%20a%20prosperous%20family%20with%20prestigious%20large-scale%20contracts%2C%20have%20little%20in%20common%20with%20the%20lives%20of%20any%20of%20the%20Vishwarkarmas%20I%20spoke%20to%20as%20they%20made%20their%20way%20to%20Ayodhya.%20This%2C%20though%2C%20is%20not%20of%20relevance.%20Even%20if%20the%20claim%20of%20their%20association%20with%20the%20Vishwakarmas%20is%20up%20for%20question%2C%20it%20is%20the%20perceived%20idea%20of%20a%20member%20of%20the%20community%20being%20accorded%20recognition%20which%20stays.%20Certainly%2C%20the%20conversation%20with%20the%20group%20made%20it%20evident%20that%20every%20symbolic%20act%2C%20gesture%2C%20and%20statement%20which%20invoked%20the%20Vishwakarma%20community%20had%20resonated%20with%20the%20community%20much%20as%20it%20was%20designed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20conversation%20with%20Rakesh%20and%20his%20group%20is%20interrupted%20by%20the%20sounds%20of%20a%20procession%2C%20with%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20increasing%20in%20volume%20as%20it%20gets%20nearer.%20There%20is%20a%20frenzy%20of%20excitement%20among%20those%20gathered%20at%20the%20roadside.%20One%20man%20shouts%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20largest%20%3Cem%3Eagarbatti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(incense%20stick)%2C%20made%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20It%E2%80%99s%20come%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20I%20saw%20it%20on%20TV.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlaring%20music%2C%20from%20speakers%20mounted%20on%20a%20long%20lorry%2C%20adorned%20with%20images%20from%20the%20Ramayana%2C%20with%20large%20cut-outs%20of%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20up%20front%2C%20the%20procession%20makes%20its%20way.%20The%20%E2%80%9Clargest%20%3Cem%3Eagarbatti%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20too%20large%20for%20the%20vehicle%2C%20sticks%20out%20from%20the%20back%20of%20the%20vehicle%2C%20and%20is%20flanked%20by%20grown%20men%20with%20their%20mouths%20painted%20red%20to%20symbolise%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20Vanar%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145517%2Fimage-1772.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221128%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145517%2Fimage-1772.png%201128w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145517%2Fimage-1772-300x188.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20145517%2Fimage-1772-1024x641.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693757%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22706%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EProcession%20carrying%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20agarbatti%20making%20its%20way%20from%20Vadodara%20to%20Ayodhya.%20Photo%3A%20Ananta%20Jain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakesh%20and%20his%20group%20say%20a%20hurried%20goodbye%20to%20walk%20along%20with%20the%20procession.%20Almost%20every%20passer-by%2C%20as%20well%20as%20our%20driver%20from%20Lucknow%2C%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eagarbatti%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20journey%20from%20Baroda%2C%20where%20it%20had%20been%20made%20by%20a%20farmer.%20The%20breathless%20reporting%20by%20the%20mainstream%20media%20has%20more%20than%20ensured%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20but%20one%20among%20a%20series%20of%20such%20processions%20winding%20its%20way%20to%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98BJP%20knows%20where%20to%20place%20the%20emphasis%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20earlier%2C%20a%20procession%20from%20Jalesar%20in%20the%20Etah%20district%20made%20its%20way%20to%20the%20town%2C%20carrying%20what%20was%20being%20described%20as%20the%20largest%20%3Cem%3Eghanta%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bell)%2C%20six-feet%20tall%2C%20weighting%202%2C100%20kilograms%2C%20supposedly%20made%20of%20Ashtadhatu%2C%20which%20was%20to%20be%20placed%20at%20the%20main%20temple.%20The%20bell%20had%20been%20dispatched%20by%20S.P.%20Baghel%2C%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Agra.%20Several%20Facebook%20posts%20spoke%20of%20the%20event%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20special%20pride%20for%20the%20Pal-Dangar%20communities%2C%20traditionally%20known%20as%20shepherd%20castes%2C%20of%20which%20Baghel%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20prominent%20representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20January%2022%20event%2C%20among%20the%20endless%20rituals%20and%20ceremonies%20being%20tracked%20by%20the%20mainstream%20media%2C%20the%20series%20of%20events%20held%20by%20caste%20groups%20and%20leaders%20of%20the%20most%20backward%20castes%20have%20largely%20been%20overlooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20engaging%20with%20these%20communities%2C%20and%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20scripted%20its%20meteoric%20rise%20and%20return%20to%20power%20by%20mobilising%20the%20votes%20of%20%3Cem%3Eati%20pichri%20jaatis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20the%20EBCs.%20This%20strategy%20involves%20carefully%20cultivating%20%3Cem%3Ebhavna%3C%2Fem%3E%20(faith)%2C%20mythology%2C%20and%20iconography.%20The%20party%20knows%20where%20to%20place%20the%20emphasis.%20It%20has%20highlighted%20the%20Vishwakarma%20as%20temple%20architects%2C%20or%20the%20Prajapati%20or%20%3Cem%3Ekumhar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20potter%20community)%20linked%20to%20the%20temple%20through%20the%20diyas%20(earthen%20lamps)%20they%20craft%2C%20despite%20this%20being%20only%20one%20aspect%20of%20their%20work%20and%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Prajapati%2C%20convenor%20of%20the%20Prajapati-Kumhar%20Samanvay%20Samiti%2C%20echoes%20this%20idea%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%20has%20asked%20every%20household%20to%20light%20a%20diya%20on%20January%2022.%20It%20has%20given%20our%20community%20work%20like%20never%20before.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20tells%20me%20the%20Samanway%20Samiti%20was%20formed%20on%20December%2023%20when%2083%20Prajapati%20sangathans%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20across%20party%20lines%20came%20together%20at%20Ambedkar%20Bhawan%20in%20Delhi%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20do%20%3Cem%3Eekikaran%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20term%20used%20for%20the%20attempt%20to%20bring%20related%20sub-castes%20under%20one%20community%20platform.%20He%20was%20elected%20national%20convenor%2C%20and%20while%20he%20claims%20the%20Samiti%20is%20non-political%2C%20he%20calls%20himself%20%E2%80%9CBJP-minded%E2%80%9D%20and%20says%20his%20community%20has%20long%20been%20moving%20towards%20the%20party.%20The%20Samiti%20organised%20a%20%E2%80%9CPrajapati%20Khichdi%E2%80%9D%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2016%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20such%20community%20leaders%2C%20he%20does%20not%20want%20it%20to%20seem%20that%20their%20supporters%20can%20be%20taken%20for%20granted%20through%20mere%20acts%20of%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20community%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20but%20just%20the%20temple%20will%20not%20assure%20the%20party%20our%20votes.%20In%20the%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20we%20will%20put%20our%20two%20dominant%20demands%20to%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20firstly%2C%20to%20give%20us%20reservations%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20category%2C%20which%20we%20deserve%2C%20and%20secondly%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%3Cem%3E%20bhagyadari%3C%2Fem%3E%20(participation)%2C%20which%20we%20do%20not%20have%20%5Bcurrently%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20familiar%20demands%20of%20several%20marginalised%20OBC%20communities%2C%20but%20amidst%20the%20fervour%20and%20emotion%2C%20they%20have%20taken%20a%20backseat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20paradox%20of%20importance%20and%20%3Cem%3Esamman%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20overlooking%20gains%20and%20losses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Kumhar%20basti%2C%20located%20in%20Bachra%20Sultanpur%2C%20Ayodhya%2C%20where%20in%20every%20house%2C%20potters%20are%20at%20work%2C%20their%20wares%20displayed%20on%20the%20cemented%20platorms%20in%20front%20of%20their%20homes%2C%20Parag%20Prajapati%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20made%20all%20Hindus%20proud%20by%20giving%20back%20the%20temple.%20For%20the%20Kumhar%20community%2C%20he%20has%20also%20given%20us%20more%20earnings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Anil%2C%20Parag%20is%20convinced%20that%20Modi%20had%20the%20Prajapati%20caste%20in%20mind%20when%20he%20asked%20the%20nation%20to%20light%20diyas%20on%20January%2022.%20As%20he%20ends%20his%20statement%2C%20several%20other%20potters%20join%20in%20with%20a%20chorus%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ayodhya%20laut%20rahein%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Ram%20is%20returning%20to%20Ayodhya)%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20154151%2Fimage-1776.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221132%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20154151%2Fimage-1776.png%201132w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20154151%2Fimage-1776-300x197.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20154151%2Fimage-1776-1024x674.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693761%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22745%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EParag%20Prajapati%E2%80%99s%20family%20at%20work%2C%20Kumhar%20Basti%2C%20Bacchra%20Sultanpur%2C%20Ayodhya.%20Photo%3A%20Ananta%20Jain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20those%20from%20the%20EBC%20communities%2C%20who%20are%20not%20wholehearted%20participants%20in%20the%20fervour%20around%20the%20temple%2C%20can%20see%20how%20potent%20is%20its%20impact.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20it%20used%20to%20be%20Mandal%20versus%20Kamandal%2C%20but%20Shah%20and%20Modi%20have%20absorbed%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20Mandal%20into%20Kamandal%2C%20a%20journey%20in%20which%20the%20Ram%20temple%20has%20taken%20centre%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amarjeet%20Nishad%2C%20who%20lives%20at%20the%20Mallha%20basti%2C%20in%20Nirmali%20Kund%2C%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20river%20Sarayu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20was%20evoking%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20movement%20of%20the%201990s%2C%20which%20initially%20brought%20the%20EBCs%20into%20the%20Sangh%20and%20BJP%20fold%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20dominant%20OBCs%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Yadavs%2C%20who%20supported%20parties%20of%20their%20own.%20During%20that%20period%2C%20the%20BJP%20intensified%20its%20focus%20on%20the%20non-dominant%20OBC%20vote%2C%20accentuating%20the%20divide%20between%20the%20two%20categories%20of%20OBC%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20temple%20now%20acts%20to%20subsume%20even%20these%20contradictions.%20A%20considerable%20number%20of%20dominant%20OBCs%20also%20respond%20to%20this%20appeal.%20This%20strategy%20goes%20beyond%20electoral%20politics%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20Sangh.%20It%20serves%20to%20consolidate%20a%20broader%20Hindu%20identity%2C%20a%20more%20homogenous%20identity%2C%20aided%20by%20the%20notion%20of%20a%20common%20Muslim%20enemy%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20a%20subtext%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20movement%20and%20its%20assault%20on%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmarjeet%20Nishad%20was%20a%20ward%20member%20from%20this%20area%2C%20but%20though%20his%20term%20ended%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20there%20have%20been%20no%20elections%20since%20then.%20A%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20member%2C%20influenced%20by%20Kanshi%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20he%20would%20like%20to%20see%20%E2%80%9CBahujan%E2%80%9D%20politics%2C%20but%20he%20says%20there%20are%20now%20few%20takers%20for%20that%20%3Cem%3Evichardhara%3C%2Fem%3E%20(idealogy)%20in%20his%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20community%20members%2C%20people%20in%20my%20own%20family%20are%20not%20able%20to%20see%20our%20own%20poverty.%20What%20they%E2%80%99re%20responding%20to%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20a%20Majhi%20home%20where%20he%20invited%20Meera%20Majhi%20to%20attend%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20They%20are%20celebrating%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20building%20of%20a%20religious-tourist%20circuit%20at%20Sringaverpur%2C%20where%20it%20installed%20a%20massive%20statue%20of%20the%20meeting%20of%20Ram%20and%20Nishad%20Raj%20Guha%2C%20our%20king.%20There%E2%80%99s%20also%20jubilation%20at%20the%20news%20that%20the%20main%20complex%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%20will%20also%20have%20a%20temple%20for%20Nishad%20Raj.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20points%20to%20one%20side%20of%20the%20Nishad%20basti%2C%20which%20was%20demolished%20to%20widen%20the%20road%20for%20the%20sacred%2014%20Kosi%20route.%20The%20tea%20stalls%20owned%20by%20the%20fishermen%20community%20are%20also%20going%20to%20be%20razed%20soon%2C%20says%20Amarjeet%2C%20adding%20the%20move%20would%20cause%20more%20people%20in%20his%20community%20to%20be%20displaced%20and%20without%20a%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20tragedy%20of%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20any%20sense%20of%20importance%20and%20%3Cem%3Esamman%3C%2Fem%3E%20makes%20us%20oblivious%20to%20what%20we%20have%20gained%20and%20what%20we%20have%20lost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20community%20always%20revered%20Nishad%20Raj%2C%20but%20now%20we%20see%20our%20King%2C%20our%20Lord%2C%20being%20given%20a%20place%20in%20the%20mainstream%2C%20in%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20own%20temple.%20It%20has%20a%20huge%20resonance.%20It%20is%20hard%20to%20focus%20on%20ground%20realities%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20all%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amarjeet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20160433%2Fimage-1777.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221132%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20160433%2Fimage-1777.png%201132w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20160433%2Fimage-1777-300x