Fi.insider.com%2F659d84086979d7371821b79a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221082%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESuzy%20Karadsheh%2C%20author%20of%20the%20Mediterranean%20Dish%2C%20is%20sometimes%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Parsley%20Queen%26quot%3B%20by%20staff%20because%20of%20her%20love%20for%20using%20the%20simple%20herb%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20recipes.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Karadsheh%2FCaitlin%20Bensel%2FThe%20Mediterranean%20Dish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20simple%20herb%20can%20take%20your%20home%20cooking%20to%20the%20next%20level%20of%20flavor%20according%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BParsley%20Queen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChopped%20parsley%20leafs%20and%20stems%20can%20add%20depth%20to%20soups%2C%20salads%2C%20and%20other%20healthy%20meals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Mediterranean%20diet%20is%20all%20about%20using%20accessible%2C%20wholesome%20ingredients%20to%20make%20delicious%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20most%20people%2C%20Suzy%20Karadsheh%20is%20known%20as%20the%20best-selling%20author%20of%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themediterraneandish.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20Dish%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20food%20blog%20and%20New%20York%20Times%20best%20selling%20cookbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20her%20staff%20and%20friends%2C%20she's%20better%20known%20as%20the%20Parsley%20Queen%2C%20an%20affectionate%20hat%20tip%20to%20her%20habit%20of%20using%20the%20herb%20in%20just%20about%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20ever%20use%20parsley%20just%20as%20a%20little%20garnish%20on%20top.%20I'm%20using%20the%20whole%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Karadsheh%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20simple%20ingredient%20can%20add%20major%20flavor%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20recipes%2C%20helping%20even%20beginner%20cooks%20to%20make%20delicious%2C%20wholesome%20meals%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFresh%20parsley%20can%20enhance%20Mediterranean%20diet%20meals%20such%20as%20healthy%20soups%20and%20salads%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKaradsheh%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20Egypt's%20Port%20Said%2C%20said%20she's%20passionate%20about%20sharing%20the%20simple%2C%20nourishing%20recipes%20she's%20eaten%20her%20whole%20life%2C%20particularly%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmediterrean-diet-healthiest-best-overall-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20a%20popular%20buzzword%20for%20healthy%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Mediterranean%20cooking%20is%20all%20about%20building%20big%20flavors%20from%20simple%2C%20fresh%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParsley%20is%20a%20perfect%20example%20%E2%80%94%20the%20humble%20herb%20was%20once%20relegated%20to%20a%20decorative%20sprig%20on%20the%20plate.%20However%2C%20finely%20chopping%20the%20stems%20and%20leaves%20can%20add%20a%20surprising%20amount%20of%20savor%20and%20complexity%20to%20the%20finished%20dish%2C%20according%20to%20Karadsheh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20key%20ingredient%20in%20healthy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-zones-minestrone-recipe-delicious-full-of-longevity-boosting-foods-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eminestrone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20classic%20Italian%20dish%20many%20people%20picture%20when%20they%20think%20of%20Mediterranean%20food.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favoid-most-common-mistakes-following-mediterranean-diet-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20diet%20also%20includes%20more%20than%2020%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20diverse%20cuisines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELearning%20to%20use%20simple%20building%20blocks%20of%20flavor%2C%20including%20fresh%20herbs%20like%20parsley%2C%20is%20essential%20to%20elevating%20wholesome%20home-cooked%20meals%2C%20according%20to%20Karadsheh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20end%20the%20pot%20of%20soup%20or%20whatever%20I'm%20mak