he%20BJP%20government%20was%20given%2C%20highlighting%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20in%20this%20period%2C%20including%20that%20to%20provide%20LPG%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20450%20to%20Ujjwala%20and%20below%20poverty%20line%20(BPL)%20beneficiaries%2C%20formation%20of%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20to%20prevent%20paper%20leaks%20and%20creation%20of%20an%20anti-gangster%20task%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20restored%20the%20general%20consent%20given%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20for%20probing%20cases%20in%20the%20state%20without%20requiring%20permission%20from%20the%20state%20government%20for%20each%20case%2C%20according%20to%20the%20release.%20Back%20in%202020%2C%20during%20the%20previous%20Congress%20government%20had%20withdrawn%20its%20general%20consent%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20had%20to%20take%20case-by-case%20consent%20from%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20meeting%20of%20the%20council%20of%20ministers%2C%20it%20was%20also%20decided%20that%20a%20committee%20would%20be%20formed%20to%20review%20the%20decisions%20taken%20by%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot-led%20previous%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months%20of%20its%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20has%20been%20just%20over%20a%20month%20since%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20was%20ousted%20in%20early%20December%2C%20among%20the%20major%20decisions%20of%20the%20newly-formed%20BJP%20government%20in%20this%20month-long%20period%20are%20those%20on%20renaming%20or%20discontinuing%20schemes%20of%20its%20predecessor%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2025%2C%2010%20days%20after%20chief%20minister%20Sharma%20took%20oath%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Economics%20and%20Statistics%20issued%20an%20office%20order%20saying%20that%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Yuva%20Mitra%20Internship%20Programme%20which%20was%20functional%20since%202021-22%2C%20is%20being%20ended%20with%20an%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20the%20Peace%20and%20Non-Violence%20Department%20%E2%80%93%20a%20brainchild%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20%E2%80%93%20issued%20another%20order%2C%20cancelling%20the%20recruitment%20process%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Seva%20Prerak%20with%20immediate%20effect%20and%20also%20withdrawing%20an%20advertisement%20dating%20back%20to%20August%202023%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Seva%20Prerak%20scheme%20was%20announced%20by%20Gehlot%20during%20his%20budget%20announcement%20in%20early%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20proposed%20to%20engage%2050%2C000%20local%20young%20men%20and%20women%20as%20%E2%80%98Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Seva%20Prerak%E2%80%99%20on%20honorarium%20for%20each%20village%20and%20urban%20ward.%20They%20will%20help%20needy%20families%20to%20avail%20benefit%20from%20Government%20schemes%20along%20with%20delivering%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20message%20of%20peace%20and%20harmony%20to%20every%20family%20in%20the%20entire%20State.%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Library%20and%20Constitution%20Centres%20will%20also%20be%20run%20by%20these%20Seva%20Preraks%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gehlot%20had%20announced%20in%20his%20budget%20speech%20on%20February%2010%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20government%20has%20also%20changed%20the%20name%20of%20Indira%20Rasoi%20Yojana%2C%20an%20initiative%20that%20offers%20meals%20to%20the%20public%20at%20a%20concessional%20rate%2C%20to%20Shree%20Annapurna%20Rasoi%20Yojana.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Annapurna%20Rasoi%20Yojana%20was%20originally%20started%20in%202016%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20led%20by%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20but%20after%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Gehlot%20administration%20renamed%20it%20as%20Indira%20Rasoi%20Yojana%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20recruitment%20for%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Seva%20Prerak%20scheme%20was%20still%20under%20process%20when%20it%20was%20cancelled%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20end%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Yuva%20Mitra%20Internship%20scheme%20has%20resulted%20in%20protests%20from%20more%20than%204%2C000%20youngsters%20who%20were%20engaged%20under%20the%20scheme%20and%20have%20lost%20their%20monthly%20income.%20The%20BJP%20has%20increased%20the%20subsidy%20per%20plate%20on%20the%20scheme%20after%20renaming%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Yuva%20Mitra%20Internship%20scheme%2C%20our%20job%20would%20involve%20promoting%20the%20various%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20the%20central%20and%20the%20state%20government.%20Every%20month%20we%20got%20paid%20around%20Rs%2017%2C500.%20After%20the%20scheme%20was%20suddenly%20ended%2C%20around%204%2C200%20youngsters%20became%20unemployed.%20We%20would%20earlier%20use%20the%20money%20to%20run%20our%20families.%20For%20nearly%20a%20month%20we%20have%20been%20protesting%20but%20our%20requests%20to%20the%20government%20have%20not%20resulted%20in%20a%20positive%20outcome.%20We%20want%20the%20government%20to%20absorb%20us%20in%20the%20network%20of%20contractual%20employees%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2025-year-old%20Dilip%20Sapera%2C%20a%20protesting%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Yuva%20Mitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20in%20opposition%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20raised%20objections%20over%20the%20Yuva%20Mitra%20Internship%20Scheme%20after%20it%20was%20announced%20by%20former%20CM%20Gehlot%20in%20his%20budget%20speech%20of%202021-22.%20The%20BJP%20had%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20using%20the%20Yuva%20Mitras%20to%20propagate%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Rajasthan%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Sachin%20Pilot%20visited%20the%20protest%20site%20of%20the%20agitating%20Yuva%20Mitras%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20reinstate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFive%20thousand%20youngsters%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20their%20jobs.%20I%20condemn%20what%20is%20happening%20with%20these%20youngsters%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20it%20is%20my%20request%20to%20the%20government%20to%20reconsider%20and%20give%20them%20their%20jobs%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pilot%20told%20reporters%20after%20meeting%20the%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20general%20secretary%20and%20spokesperson%20Swarnim%20Chaturvedi%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20trying%20to%20benefit%20people%20of%20its%20ideology%20by%20bringing%20back%20the%20pension%20for%20MISA%20prisoners%20while%20neglecting%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20previous%20Gehlot%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20continues%20to%20maintain%20its%20stand%20that%20the%20Yuva%20Mitras%20were%20used%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20promote%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20were%20jailed%20during%20the%20Emergency%20are%20freedom%20fighters%20who%20stood%20up%20for%20democracy%20as%20the%20Congress%20party%20ended%20it%20by%20imposing%20the%20Emergency.%20The%20Congress%20government%20had%20stopped%20their%20pension%2C%20which%20we%20have%20revived%20after%20coming%20to%20power.%20As%20for%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Yuva%20Mitras%2C%20their%20only%20task%20was%20to%20retweet%20the%20tweets%20of%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20promote%20the%20Congress%20party%20while%20getting%20money%20from%20the%20state%20exchequer.%20The%20Congress%20appointed%20its%20own%20workers%20and%20office%20bearers%20by%20the%20name%20of%20Yuva%20Mitras%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20BJP%20state%20spokesperson%20Laxmikant%20Bhardwaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20protesters%20refute%20the%20allegations%2C%20even%20urging%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20the%20scheme%20but%20continue%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20appointed%20after%20due%20process%20of%20screening%2C%20written%20examinations%2C%20and%20interviews.%20There%20is%20no%20truth%20to%20the%20allegations%20that%20we