22Taking%20to%20Instagram%2C%20Shoaib%20Malik%20captioned%20a%20few%20pictures%20from%20his%20wedding%20with%20Sana%20Javed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actor%20Rashmilka%20Mandanna's%20Deepfake%20Creator%20Arrested%20In%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20responsible%20for%20actor%20Rashmika%20Mandanna's%20deepfake%20video%20was%20arrested%20today%2C%20Delhi%20police%20said.%C2%A0The%20video%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20in%20November%20last%20year%2C%20prompting%20widespread%20calls%20for%20regulations%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deepfake%20video%20in%20question%20initially%20showcased%20British-Indian%20influencer%20Zara%20Patel%2C%20entering%20a%20lift%20in%20a%20black%20outfit.%20However%2C%20through%20the%20use%20of%20deepfake%20technology%2C%20Ms%20Patel's%20face%20seamlessly%20morphed%20into%20that%20of%20Ms%20Mandanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftime-for-platforms-to-take-responsibility-minister-ashwini-vaishnaw-to-ndtv-on-deepfakes-4882265%5C%22%3ETime%20For%20Platforms%20To%20Take%20Responsibility%3A%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20To%20NDTV%20On%20Deepfakes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20her%20dismay%2C%20Ms%20Mandanna%20described%20the%20ordeal%20as%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20scary%26quot%3B%20and%20highlighted%20the%20vulnerability%20individuals%20face%20due%20to%20the%20misuse%20of%20technology.%20%26quot%3BSomething%20like%20this%20is%20honestly%2C%20extremely%20scary%20not%20only%20for%20me%20but%20also%20for%20each%20one%20of%20us%20who%20today%20is%20vulnerable%20to%20so%20much%20harm%20because%20of%20how%20technology%20is%20being%20misused%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20remarked%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aftermath%20of%20the%20viral%20deepfake%20video%20prompted%20the%20Centre%20to%20issue%20an%20advisory%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20stressing%20the%20legal%20provisions%20covering%20deepfakes%20and%20the%20potential%20penalties%20associated%20with%20their%20creation%20and%20circulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeepfake-artificial-intelligence-ndtv-explains-what-is-a-deepfake-and-how-you-can-spot-it-4599193%5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20A%20Deepfake%20And%20How%20You%20Can%20Spot%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20in%20December%20met%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20review%20progress%20made%20by%20them%20in%20tackling%20misinformation%20and%20deepfakes%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20advisories%20will%20be%20issued%20in%20the%20next%20two%20days%20to%20ensure%20100%20per%20cent%20compliance%20by%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepfakes%20are%20a%20form%20of%20synthetic%20media%20crafted%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20employing%20sophisticated%20algorithms%20to%20manipulate%20both%20visual%20and%20audio%20elements.%20The%20term%20gained%20prominence%20in%202017%20when%20a%20Reddit%20user%20introduced%20a%20platform%20for%20sharing%20manipulated%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20deepfake%20technology%20has%20evolved%2C%20becoming%20a%20potential%20weapon%20for%20cybercriminals%20to%20disrupt%20and%20damage%20the%20reputation%20of%20individuals%2C%20companies%2C%20or%20even%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20IT%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said%20recently%20that%20notices%20were%20sent%20to%20all%20social%20media%20companies%20directing%20them%20to%20take%20necessary%20steps%20to%20identify%20and%20remove%20disinformation%20from%20their%20platforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepfake%20is%20a%20big%20issue%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20We%20recently%20issued%20notices%20to%20all%20the%20big%20social%20media%20forms%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20identify%20deepfakes%2C%20for%20removing%20those%20content.%20The%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20responded.%20They%20are%20taking%20action.%20We%20have%20told%20them%20to%20be%20more%20aggressive%20in%20this%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20we%20must%20notice%20that%20the%20'Safe%20Harbour'%20Clause%20that%20most%20of%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20been%20enjoying%2C%20doesn't%20apply%20if%20the%20platforms%20do%20not%20take%20adequate%20steps%20to%20remove%20the%20deepfakes%20from%20their%20platforms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Ms%20Mandanna%2C%20deepfake%20videos%20of%20Katrina%20Kaif%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Priyanka%20Chopra%20and%20even%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20the%20internet%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705740300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fmduc9nhg_-rashmika-_625x300_01_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-who-made-actor-rashmika-mandannas-deepfake-arrested-by-delhi-police-4898196%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20man%20responsible%20for%20actor%20Rashmika%20Mandanna's%20deepfake%20video%20was%20arrested%20today%2C%20Delhi%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-who-made-actor-rashmika-mandannas-deepfake-arrested-by-delhi-police-4898196%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-who-made-actor-rashmika-mandannas-deepfake-arrested-by-delhi-police-4898196%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-who-made-actor-rashmika-mandannas-deepfake-arrested-by-delhi-police-4898196%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan%20Anyone%20Be%20More%20Corrupt%20Than%20Gandhis%26quot%3B%3A%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp