0as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20state%20Social%20Welfare%20Department%20and%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20issued%20a%20'last%20opportunity'%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20(ED)%20to%20record%20his%20statement%20on%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam%20days%20ago.%20Soren%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20replied%20to%20the%20agency%2C%20labelling%20the%20summons%20as%20'illegal.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20you%20have%20not%20come%20to%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20in%20obedience%20to%20the%20summonses%20issued%20to%20you%2C%20we%20are%20giving%20you%20this%20last%20opportunity%20to%20record%20your%20statement%20under%20section%2050%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%202002%2C%20at%20the%20place%2C%20date%20and%20time%2C%20mutually%20convenient%20to%20you%20as%20well%20as%20the%20undersigned%20(ED)%2C%20which%20should%20be%20within%207%20days%20of%20receipt%20of%20this%20notice%2FSummons%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20ED%20in%20its%20summons.%3Cbr%3E%5CnSoren%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20ED%20earlier%20in%20mid-August%2C%202023%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20land%20'scam'%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20CM%20ignored%20the%20summons%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20was%20busy%20with%20the%20state's%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations.%20He%20was%20asked%20again%20to%20appear%20on%20August%2024%20and%20September%209%20but%20he%20skipped%20the%20dates%2C%20citing%20preoccupations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20then%20issued%20its%20fourth%20summons%20to%20the%20Jharkhand%20CM%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20report%20to%20the%20agency%20on%20September%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20agency%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20said%20he%20had%20provided%20all%20necessary%20documents%20and%20information%20to%20the%20ED.%20He%20wrote%20that%20if%20the%20ED%20needed%20any%20information%2C%20it%20could%20refer%20to%20the%20documents%20that%20