women.org%2Fen%2Fnews-stories%2Fstatement%2F2024%2F01%2Fstatement-on-gaza-by-un-women-executive-director-sima-bahous%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20statement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20alongside%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20failure%2C%20and%20the%20generational%20trauma%20inflicted%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20over%20these%20100%20days%20and%20counting%2C%20will%20haunt%20all%20of%20us%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20of%207th%20October%20and%20the%20horrors%20that%20have%20followed%2C%20especially%20in%20Gaza%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20evidenced%20once%20more%20that%20women%20and%20children%20are%20the%20first%20victims%20of%20conflict.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatement%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Funwomenchief%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40unwomenchief%3C%2Fa%3E%20Sima%20Bahous%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRWf2vhOI7E%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRWf2vhOI7E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5a9jgKFvyK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5a9jgKFvyK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UN%20Women%20(%40UN_Women)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN_Women%2Fstatus%2F1748360205698515306%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Women%20also%20reiterated%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20accounts%20of%20unconscionable%20sexual%20violence%20and%20other%20gender-based%20violence%20during%20the%20Hamas-led%20attacks%20against%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20that%20sparked%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20called%20for%20accountability%2C%20justice%20and%20support%20for%20all%20those%20affected%20and%20for%20the%20immediate%20and%20unconditional%20release%20of%20all%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Impossible%20decisions%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Women%20said%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%20%E2%80%9Cis%20fundamentally%20a%20protection%20crisis%20for%20women%E2%80%9D%20at%20a%20time%20when%20nowhere%20in%20the%20enclave%20is%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%201.9%20million%20people%20now%20displaced%2C%20close%20to%20a%20million%20are%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cimpossible%20decisions%E2%80%9D%20they%20have%20to%20make%20regarding%20whether%20to%20evacuate%20%E2%80%93%20when%20and%20how%20as%20well%20as%20where%20to%20go%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Care%20entrenched%20with%20gender%20differentiated%20fears%20and%20experiences%E2%80%9D%2C%20given%20risks%20of%20attacks%20and%20harassment%20while%20on%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Women%20further%20estimated%20that%20at%20least%203%2C000%20women%20may%20have%20become%20widows%20and%20heads%20of%20households%2C%20and%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20children%20may%20now%20be%20fatherless.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20more%20women%20fear%20families%20will%20resort%20to%20desperate%20coping%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20early%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20organisations%20continue%20to%20operate%20amidst%20the%20crisis.%20In%20November%2C%20UN%20Women%20conducted%20a%20rapid%20survey%20of%2012%20women-led%20organisations%20and%20one%20youth-led%20group%20which%20found%20that%20most%20%E2%80%93%2083%25%20%E2%80%93%20were%20at%20least%20partially%20operating%2C%20focused%20mainly%20on%20the%20emergency%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20funding%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fflash-appeal-2023-glance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20Flash%20Appeal%20for%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20directly%20gone%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStaying%20the%20course%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20part%20of%20UN%20Women%E2%80%99s%20six-month%20response%20plan%20for%20Gaza%2C%20which%20includes%20providing%20emergency%20food%20assistance%20to%20over%2014%2C000%20female-headed%20households%20and%20supporting%20the%20distribution%20of%20items%20requested%20by%20women%20on%20the%20ground%20such%20as%20clothing%2C%20sanitary%20products%20and%20baby%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20is%20also%20partnering%20with%20women-led%20organizations%20to%20deliver%20gender%20responsive%20services%20for%20gender-based%20violence%2C%20establishing%20women-led%20protection%20and%20response%20committees%20in%20shelters%20and%20convening%20regular%20consultations%20with%20women%E2%80%99s%20organizations%20to%20discuss%20the%20challenges%20they%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F01%2F1145707%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3EUN%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705736107000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06132249%2FCooking-in-war.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftwo-mothers-killed-each-hour-in-gaza-conflict-un-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Women%20and%20children%20account%20for%20roughly%2070%25%20of%20people%20killed%20in%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20with%20two%20mothers%20killed%20every%20hour%20since%20hostilities%20erupted%20more%20than%20100%20days%20ago%2C%20according%20to%20a%20UN%20Women%20report%20published%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftwo-mothers-killed-each-hour-in-gaza-conflict-un-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%