rested-for-allegedly-recording-minor-girls-in-washroom%2Farticleshow%2F107007200.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107007200.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EEstes%20Carter%20Thompson%20III%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20for%20American%20Airlines%2C%20was%20arrested%20for%20attempting%20to%20secretly%20record%20a%2014-year-old%20female%20passenger%20who%20was%20using%20the%20bathroom.%20He%20is%20also%20facing%20charges%20for%20possessing%20recordings%20of%20four%20other%20minor%20female%20passengers.%20Thompson%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20attempted%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20children%20and%20possession%20of%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20images.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Famerican-airlines-flight-attendant-arrested-for-allegedly-recording-minor-girls-in-washroom%2Farticleshow%2F107007200.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Famerican-airlines-flight-attendant-arrested-for-allegedly-recording-minor-girls-in-washroom%2Famp_articleshow%2F107007200.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Famerican-airlines-flight-attendant-arrested-for-allegedly-recording-minor-girls-in-washroom%2Famp_articleshow%2F107007200.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boris%20Johnson%20claims%20the%20world%20would%20be%20'more%20stable%20under%20Trump'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705735080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F05%2F768x432%2Fskynews-boris-johnson-donald-trump_6168649.jpg%3F20230526152806%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fboris-johnson-claims-the-world-would-be-more-stable-under-donald-trump-13052064%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boris%20Johnson%20has%20endorsed%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20the%20US%20presidency%2C%20claiming%20he%20will%20surprise%20his%20critics%20and%20back%20Ukraine%2C%20making%20%26quot%3Bthe%20West%20stronger%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world%20more%20stable%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fboris-johnson-claims-the-world-would-be-more-stable-under-donald-trump-13052064%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fboris-johnson-claims-the-world-would-be-more-stable-under-donald-trump-13052064%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fboris-johnson-claims-the-world-would-be-more-stable-under-donald-trump-13052064%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20Hard%20Realities%20Will%20Soon%20Catch%20Up%20With%20Maldives%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFractious%20and%20divided%20internal%20politics%2C%20Islamism%20and%20the%20Chinese%20hand%20explain%20the%20antagonism%20of%20the%20new%20government%20of%20Maldives%20towards%20India.%20The%20government%20before%20it%2C%20the%20Solih%20government%2C%20made%20%26quot%3BIndia%20First%26quot%3B%20its%20foreign%20policy%20priority.%20This%20was%20a%20reversal%20of%20the%20policy%20of%20the%20government%20that%20preceded%20it%2C%20the%20Abdulla%20Yameen%20government%2C%20which%20prioritised%20China%20and%20cold-shouldered%20India.%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%2C%20now%20President%2C%20made%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Out%26quot%3B%20his%20campaign%20slogan%2C%20reverting%20even%20more%20emphatically%20to%20the%20anti-Indian%20stance%20of%20the%20Yameen%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENormally%2C%20in%20any%20country%20with%20mature%20politics%2C%20the%20country's%20longer%20term%20foreign%20policy%20interests%20should%20not%20become%20a%20victim%20of%20domestic%20politics.%20India%20is%20next%20door%2C%20it%20has%20provided%20assistance%20to%20the%20Maldives%20at%20critical%20moments.%20In%201988%2C%20it%20saved%20the%20Gayoom%20government%20from%20a%20coup%20attempt.%20India%20has%20shown%20its%20ability%20to%20be%20a%20first%20responder%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20area%20when%20natural%20disasters%20have%20struck.%20It%20assisted%20the%20Maldives%20when%20the%20Tsunami%20struck%20it%20in%202004%2C%20when%20the%20nation%20faced%20a%20water%20crisis%20in%202014%2C%20by%20providing%20300%2C000%20doses%20of%20vaccine%20when%20a%20measles%20outbreak%20was%20feared%20in%202020%2C%20and%2C%20when%20on%2020%20January%202021%2C%20Maldives%20was%20the%20first%20country%20to%20receive%20a%20gift%20of%20100%2C000%20doses%20of%20India-manufactured%20vaccines%2C%20followed%20by%20two%20other%20consignments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20developed%20several%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20Maldives.%20It%20is%20currently%20involved%20in%20the%20largest-ever%20infrastructure%20project-%20the%20Greater%20Male%20Connectivity%20project.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20Hanimaadhoo%20International%20Airport%20Development%20project%2C%20a%20new%20terminal%20is%20being%20built%20under%20an%20Indian%20credit%20line.In%20the%20healthcare%20sector%2C%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Memorial%20Hospital%2C%20built%20with%20Indian%20assistance%2C%20is%20being%20further%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20active%20in%20the%20education%20sector%2C%20in%20technical%20education%2C%20training%20to%20Maldivian%20teachers%20and%20vocational%20training%20for%20the%20youth.The%20majority%20of%20the%20expatriate%20teachers%20in%20Maldives%20are%20Indian%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%2C%20a%20collection%20of%20widely%20dispersed%201%2C192%20islands%2C%20of%20which%20only%20187%20are%20inhabited%2C%20possesses%20a%20large%20EEZ%20of%20923%2C322%20square%20kilometres.%20It%20needs%20to%20monitor%20the%20EEZ%20and%20ensure%20its%20maritime%20security.%20India%20has%20been%20a%20longstanding%20partner%20in%20assisting%20Maldives%20in%20meeting%20this%20requirement.%20Since%201988%2C%20defence%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Maldives%20has%20expanded.%20During%20Mohamed%20Nasheed's%20presidency%20(2008-2012)%2C%20India%20provided%20radars%2C%20helicopters%20and%20a%20military%20hospital.%20India%20also%20provides%20medical%20training%20and%20humanitarian%20and%20disaster%20response%20assistance%2C%20help%20with%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations%2C%20medical%20evacuations.%20hydrographic%20mapping%20and%20maritime%20domain%20awareness.%20Indian%20pilots%20and%20engineers%20operate%20the%20Dornier%20aircraft%20and%20the%20Dhruv%20helicopters.%20All%20the%20India-aided%20facilities%20and%20platforms%20operate%20directly%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Maldives%20National%20Defence%20Force%20(MNDF).%20The%20number%20of%20Indian%20defence%20personnel%20in%20Maldives%20is%20very%20small-%20about%2075.%20India%20offers%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20training%20opportunities%20for%20the%20Maldivian%20National%20Defence%20Forces%2Cmeeting%20around%2070%25%20of%20their%20defence%20training%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20cooperation%20continued%20during%20the%20pro-China%20and%20anti-India%20regime%20of%20Abdulla%20Yameen%20(2013-2018).%20But%20President%20Muizzu%20seems%20bent%20on%20excluding%20any%20Indian%20military%20presence%20in%20Maldives%2C%20considering%20it%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20national%20security.%20This%20is%20absurd%20as%20India%20does%20not%20need%2075%20military%20personnel%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20threaten%20Maldives'%20security.%20More%20than%20that%20India%20has%20historically%20helped%20safeguard%20Maldives'%20security%20rather%20than%20threatening%20it%20in%20any%20way.%20Muizzu%20is%20engaging%20in%20unprincipled%20politics%20in%20response%20to%20local%20and%20external%20anti-Indian%20forces.%20He%20seeks%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20by%20March%2015.%20This%20is%20being%20negotiated.%20He%20has%20already%20revoked%20the%20Hydrographic%20Survey%20Agreement.%20The%20Maldives%20also%20skipped%20the%20latest%20meeting%20of%20the%20national%20security%20advisor-level%20Colombo%20Security%20Conclave%2C%20in%20which%20it%20is%20a%20member%20state%20along%20with%20India%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Mauritius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20Maldives%20should%20seek%20to%20unravel%20a%20relationship%20that%20is%20vital%20for%20its%20own%20interests%2C%20and%20one%20in%20which%20India%20too%20has%20stakes%20as%20a%20close%20and%20friendly%20neighbour%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20maritime%20security%2C%20is%20baffling.%20This%20spurning%20of%20India%20is%20in%20part%20also%20because%20of%20increasing%20Islamisation%20of%20Maldivian%20society.%20Numerous%20Maldivians%20joined%20the%20Islamic%20State-%20on%20a%20per%20capita%20basis%20Maldives%20contributed%20the%20largest%20number.%20Why%20an%20island%20that%20survives%20on%20international%20tourism%2C%20which%20requires%20an%20open%20and%20tolerant%20society%2C%20and%20one%20distant%20from%20the%20politics%20and%20quarrels%20of%20West%20Asia%2C%20should%20be%20increasingly%20infused%20with%20Islamist%20ideology%20is%20not%20easily%20comprehensible.%20It%20is%20this%20increasing%20Islamist%20orientation%20of%20Maldives%20that%20explains%20why%20Muizzu%20made%20his%20visit%20abroad%20to%20Turkey.%20Turkish%20president%20Erdogan%20with%20his%20close%20links%20with%20the%20Muslim%20Brotherhood%20is%20playing%20religious%20politics%20in%20our%20neighbourhood.%20Turkey%20has%20drawn%20closer%20to%20Pakistan%20as%20part%20of%20Islamic%20solidarity%20and%20Erdogan%20is%20the%20only%20leader%20that%20raises%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20in%20the%20UN.%20One%20can%20assume%20that%20Pakistan%20is%20part%20of%20the%20efforts%20to%20draw%20Maldives%20away%20from%20dependence%20on%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20foreign%20visit%20to%20Turkey%2C%20Muizzu%20made%20a%20state%20visit%20to%20China%20where%20he%20was%20feted%20by%20the%20Chinese.%20The%20two%20countries%20elevated%20their%20ties%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20strategic%20cooperative%20partnership%26quot%3B.%20This%20was%20intended%20by%20both%20sides%20to%20send%20a%20signal%20to%20India.%20The%20nuance%20here%20is%20that%20China%20is%20openly%20claiming%20a%20heightened%20strategic%20interest%20in%20Maldives.%20Several%20new%20agreements%20were%20signed%20during%20the%20visit%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20agriculture%20and%20climate%2C%20China%20is%20the%20largest%20external%20creditor%20of%20Maldives.%20The%20World%20Bank%20in%20its%20October%20report%20cautioned%20Maldives%20on%20more%20projects%20with%20China%20since%20the%20%241.37%20billion%20debt%20it%20already%20owes%20to%20China%20constitutes%20about%2020%25%20of%20its%20public%20debt.%20Maldives%20debt%20to%20India%20is%20only%20%24123%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20return%20from%20China%20%2C%20Muizzu's%20statements%20have%20become%20more%20aggressive%20and%20explicit%20in%20diluting%20ties%20with%20India.%20Maldives%20is%20critically%20dependent%20on%20basic%20food%20supplies%20from%20India%2C%20as%20well%20as%20medical%20treatment.%20He%20has%20announced%20that%20the%20country's%20healthcare%20insurance%20scheme%20will%20allow%20Maldivians%20to%20be%20treated%20in%20Thailand%20and%20Dubai%2C%20even%20if%20this%20will%20greatly%20increase%20costs.%20He%20also%20intends%20to%20import%20staple%20foods%20such%20as%20rice%2C%20sugar%20and%20flour%20from%20other%20sources%20such%20as%20Turkey.%20Whether%20this%20would%20be%20sustainable%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia-Maldives%20ties%20have%20been%20badly%20hit%20at%20the%20level%20of%20the%20Indian%20public%20by%20the%20highly%20derogatory%20remarks%20made%20by%20three%20junior%20Maldivian%20ministers%20personally%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Indian%20social%20media%20has%20expressed%20its%20outrage%20at%20the%20insults%20and%20called%20for%20a%20tourist%20boycott%20of%20Maldives.%20In%202023%2C%20India%20sent%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20tourists%20to%20the%20Maldives%20(2%2C09%2C198)%2C%20with%20around%2011.8%20%25%20market%20share.%20The%20government%20of%20India%20did%20call%20in%20the%20Maldives%20ambassador%20to%20India%20for%20a%20protest%2C%20but%20has%20otherwise%20has%20officially%20avoided%20any%20polemics%20and%20has%20sensibly%20affirmed%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20its%20development%20cooperation%20with%20Maldives.%20The%20three%20offending%20ministers%20have%20been%20suspended%20and%20the%20Maldives%20government%2C%20without%20apologising%2C%20has%20repudiated%20their%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20aware%20that%20there%20is%20also%20a%20strong%20pro-India%20constituency%20in%20Maldives.%20India%20has%20seen%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20ties%20with%20Maldives.%20It%20has%20to%20bide%20its%20time.%20Hard%20realities%20would%20catch%20up%20eventually%20with%20the%20anti-Indian%20forces.%20India%20bears%20no%20ill-will%20towards%20the%20Maldives.%20It%20has%20certain%20objective%20security%20interests%20in%20Maldives%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20maritime%20domain%2C%20especially%20with%20China's%20expansionist%20Indian%20Ocean%20policies.%20Maldives%20would%20no%20doubt%20be%20cognisant%20of%20India's%20red%20lines.%20Let's%20hope%20Muizzu%20doesn't%20overplay%20his%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kanwal%20Sibal%20was%20Foreign%20Secretary%20and%20Ambassador%20to%20Turkey%2C%20Egypt%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Russia%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Of%20Mission%20in%20Washington.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705734900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fc1nt5v2g_mohamed-muizzu_625x300_09_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhard-realities-will-soon-catch-up-with-maldives-4897793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fractious%20and%20divided%20i