e%20efforts%20to%20save%20him%2C%20Sanjay%20Shah%2C%2056%2C%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries%20during%20treatment%20while%20Mr%20Datlaa%20remains%20in%20a%20serious%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20facts%20about%20Sanjay%20Shah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%93%20Sanjay%20Shah%20was%20the%20Founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Vistex%2C%20a%20tech%20company%20that%20helps%20global%20leaders%20like%20Apple%2C%20Walmart%2C%20and%20others%20improve%20their%20revenue%20and%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%93%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20originally%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20left%20for%20Lehigh%20University%20in%20Pennsylvania%2C%20earning%20his%20MBA%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021%20in%201989.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%93%20He%20worked%20at%20PricewaterhouseCoopers%20and%20General%20Motors%20before%20moving%20to%20Germany%20to%20work%20for%20the%20software%20giant%20SAP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%93%20After%20leaving%20SAP%2C%20Sanjay%20Shah%20founded%20Vistex%2C%20guiding%20the%20company%20to%20unparalleled%20year-over-year%20growth%20for%20two%20decades%20without%20any%20external%20funding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%93%20The%20self-made%20businessman%20also%20established%20the%20Vistex%20Foundation%2C%20supporting%20health%20and%20education%20nonprofits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20donated%20%245%20million%20to%20Lehigh%20University%20for%20the%20Vistex%20Institute%20for%20Executive%20Learning%20and%20Research%2C%20mentioned%20on%20the%20University%20page.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20Vistex%20Hospital%20in%20Bihar%2C%20India%2C%20began%20serving%20the%20community%20with%20primary%20and%20secondary%20care.%20It%20was%20recognised%20as%20a%20national%20model%20Covid-19%20facility.%C2%A0The%20hospital%20is%20currently%20expanding%2C%20adding%20two%20new%20floors%20to%20enhance%20its%20facilities%20and%20contribute%20further%20to%20community%20well-being.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705734060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F9uat6ccg_sanjay-shah-_625x300_20_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsome-facts-about-vistex-ceo-sanjay-shah-who-died-in-aerial-stunt-mishap-at-company-event-4897617%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sanjay%20Shah%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Vistex%20Asia%2C%20died%20on%20Thursday%20in%20an%20accident%20at%20the%20company's%2025th-anniversary%20celebrations%20in%20Hyderabad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsome-facts-about-vistex-ceo-sanjay-shah-who-died-in-aerial-stunt-mishap-at-company-event-4897617%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsome-facts-about-vistex-ceo-sanjay-shah-who-died-in-aerial-stunt-mishap-at-company-event-4897617%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsome-facts-about-vistex-ceo-sanjay-shah-who-died-in-aerial-stunt-mishap-at-company-event-4897617%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cargo%20plane%20makes%20emergency%20landing%20shortly%20after%20takeoff%20at%20Miami%20airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705733523000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107006962%2Cimgsize-470061.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Femergency-landing-of-cargo-plane-at-miami-airport%2Farticleshow%2F107006932.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107006932.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Femergen