ent%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Popular%20Children's%20Story%20%26quot%3BFrightened%26quot%3B%20UK's%20Queen%20Camilla%20As%20A%20Child%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBritain's%20Queen%20Camilla%20recently%20revealed%20a%20popular%20children's%20story%20%26quot%3Bfrightened%26quot%3B%20her%20as%20a%20young%20child.%20Speaking%20on%20her%20new%20podcast%2C%20The%20Queen's%20Reading%20Room%2C%20the%2076-year-old%20said%20that%20she%20was%20never%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20author%20Lewis%20Carroll%20because%20'Alice%20in%20Wonderland'%20scared%20her%20when%20she%20was%20little.%20She%20admitted%20it%20was%20some%20of%20the%20characters%20that%20%26quot%3Bfrightened%26quot%3B%20her.%20She%20also%20said%20that%20she%20was%20fearful%20of%20Alice%20going%20down%20the%20rabbit%20hole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQueen%20Camilla%20was%20quizzed%20on%20whether%20she%20preferred%20Lewis%20Carroll%20or%20Hans%20Christian%20Anderson%20-%20the%20author%20of%20The%20Little%20Mermaid%20and%20The%20Ugly%20Duckling.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20awful%20thing%20to%20admit%2C%20but%20I've%20never%20really%20liked%20Lewis%20Carroll%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20rather%20put%20off%20by%20Alice%20going%20down%20that%20rabbit%20hole.%20It%20always%20really%20frightened%20me%20as%20a%20child.%20All%20the%20Mad%20Hatters%20and%20Red%20Queens%20and...%20it%20just%20wasn't%20my%20favourite%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2024%2F01%2F19%2Fi-never-liked-lewis-carroll-alice-frightened-me-says-queen%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2076-year-old%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20have%20let%20her%20own%20views%20of%20Lewis%20Carroll%20shape%20those%20of%20others.%20'Alice's%20Adventures%20in%20Wonderland'%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20books%20featured%20on%20her%20Reading%20Room%20website%2C%20recommended%20by%20authors%20William%20Boyd%2C%20Elif%20Shafak%20and%20Susan%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20actor%20Richard%20E%20Grant%20read%20Mr%20Carroll's%20'All%20in%20the%20Golden%20Afternoon'%2C%20the%20preface%20poem%20to%20'Alice%20in%20Wonderland'%2C%20at%20the%20inaugural%20Queen's%20Reading%20Room%20Literary%20Festival%20at%20Hampton%20Court%20Palace%20in%20June.%20According%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20at%20a%20poetry%20recital%20attended%20by%20the%20Queen%20at%20a%20primary%20school%20in%20west%20London%20last%20August%2C%20two%20students%20performed%20Mr%20Carroll's%20Jabberwocky%2C%20dressed%20as%20the%20Mad%20Hatter%20and%20Alice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Freddit-to-go-public-ipo-set-for-march-aiming-for-10-billion-debut-report-4894702%5C%22%3EReddit%20To%20Go%20Public%2C%20IPO%20Set%20For%20March%2C%20Aiming%20For%20%2410%20Billion%20Debut%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Queen's%20Reading%20Room%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthequeensreadingroom.co.uk%2F%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20podcast%20aims%20to%20promote%20the%20power%20and%20benefits%20of%20reading%20and%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20help%20more%20people%20find%20and%20connect%20with%20books%20which%20enrich%20their%20lives.%20It%20was%20launched%20in%202021%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20charity%2C%20we%20produce%20accessible%2C%20free%20educational%20content%20around%20literature%20365%20days%20a%20year%20through%20our%20social%20channels%20and%20website%3B%20as%20well%20as%20literary%20festivals%20and%20events%3B%20research%20and%20campaigns%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20website%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705731840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0lu7mkl8_queen-camilla-_6