2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fsasquatch-sunset-review-1235879991%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEyes%20Of%20Ram%20Lalla%20Can't%20Be%20Revealed%20Before%20Pran%20Pratishtha%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Priest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAcharya%20Satyendra%20Das%2C%20Chief%20Priest%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Temple%2C%20said%20today%20that%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20cannot%20be%20revealed%20before%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Pran%20Praishtha'%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Lalla%20will%20take%20place%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20idol%20of%20the%20lord%2C%20sculpted%20by%20Arun%20Yogiraj%2C%20was%20placed%20inside%20the%20Sanctum%20Santorum%20of%20the%20temple.%20Covered%20with%20a%20veil%2C%20the%20first%20photo%20of%20the%20idol%20was%20revealed%20during%20the%20placement%20ceremony%20in%20the%20Sanctum%20Sanctorum%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20pictures%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20showing%20his%20eyes%20surfaced%20on%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20Acharya%20Satyendra%20Das%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20eyes%20of%20Lord%20Ram's%20idol%20cannot%20be%20revealed%20before%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20is%20completed.%20The%20idol%20where%20the%20eyes%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20can%20be%20seen%20is%20not%20the%20real%20idol.%20If%20the%20eyes%20can%20be%20seen%2C%20an%20investigation%20should%20be%20done%20on%20who%20revealed%20the%20eyes%20and%20how%20the%20pictures%20of%20the%20idol%20are%20going%20viral.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20procedures%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20as%20usual.%20However%2C%20the%20eyes%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20will%20not%20be%20revealed%20until%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20procedures%20for%20carrying%20the%20tent%20idol%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Lalla%20to%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20established%20in%20the%20Sanctum%20Santorum%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20where%20the%20new%20idol%20will%20be%20installed.%20There%20is%20also%20no%20auspicious%20timing%20for%20this.%20An%20auspicious%20timing%20is%20predicted%20when%20something%20new%20has%20to%20be%20done.%20This%20is%20a%20procedure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcharya%20Das%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20question%20is%20who%20will%20carry%20the%20idol%20to%20the%20temple.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20carried%20the%20idol%20from%20the%20tent%20to%20the%20temporarily%20built%20temple.%20CM%20Yogi%20may%20himself%20carry%20the%20idol%20to%20the%20temple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%201992%2C%20when%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%20by%20the%20'Kar%20Sevaks'%2C%20they%20set%20up%20a%20small%20idol%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20a%20tent%20at%20the%20demolition%20site%20and%20started%20worshipping%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20history%20of%20the%20'tent%20idol'%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Lalla%20dates%20back%20to%201949%20when%20some%20Hindu%20leaders%20kept%20the%20idol%20inside%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%20It%20was%20later%20claimed%20that%20the%20lord%20appeared%20in%20the%20mosque%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Chief%20Priest%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Temple%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20procedures%20of%20the%20'Aunshthan'%2C%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20holding%20to%20mark%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20person%20who%20does%20'Anushthan'%20has%20to%20sleep%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20not%20to%20speak%20lies%2C%20chant%20mantras%20like%20'Gayatri%20mantra'%2C%20has%20to%20eat%20on%20a%20leaf%20and%20follow%20'Brahmacharya'%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20PM%20Modi%20himself%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20commence%20a%20special%2011-day%20'Anushthan'%20(ritual)%20ahead%20of%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%20at%20Ayodhya's%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%