ingly%2C%20even%20today%2C%20companies%20like%20Soulful%20and%20possibly%20now%20Slurp%20Farm%2C%20no%20major%20player%20has%20emerged%20in%20this%20space.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20people%20still%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20many%20options%20to%20explore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20now%20boasts%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%202.5%20crores%20and%20has%20a%20team%20of%20nine%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20numbers%20signal%20success%2C%20Sai%20emphasised%20the%20patience%20required%20to%20reach%20this%20point.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20slow%20burn%20for%20us%3B%20the%20industry%20is%20still%20nascent%2C%20and%20people%20are%20only%20now%20beginning%20to%20open%20up.%20Back%20in%202013%2C%20when%20I%20started%20my%20research%2C%20there%20were%20no%20avenues%20available.%20Institutes%20dedicated%20to%20this%20cause%20were%20scarce%2C%20and%20the%20technology%20to%20do%20simple%20things%20like%20making%20uttapam%20from%20jowar%20was%20not%20readily%20accessible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CTimes%20have%20changed%20significantly%20since%20then.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%20dedicated%20institutes%20for%20research%2C%20and%20more%20individuals%20are%20investing%20in%20millet-based%20startups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20year%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305138%2Fmasterchef-india-contestant-whips-up-gluten-free-desserts-in-her-house-of-millets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einitiative%20for%20millets%20%3C%2Fa%3Elast%20year%20has%20undoubtedly%20made%20a%20positive%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20believe%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%20in%20the%20awareness%20stage%20rather%20than%20a%20point%20where%20a%20habit%20has%20been%20fully%20formed.%20People%20are%20trying%2C%20and%20experimenting%2C%20but%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20become%20a%20daily%