ne%20I%20was%20innocent%2C%20but%20my%20own%20parents%20did%20not%20believe%20me.%20I%20was%20getting%20depressed%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20one%20day%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20then-commissioner%20of%20police%20V%20C%20Sajjanar.%20A%20conversation%20with%20him%20gave%20Murthy%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20being%20a%20victim%20to%20protecting%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20contacts%20were%20among%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%201%2C500%20contacts%2C%20he%20had%20also%20received%20similar%20messages%20from%20the%20criminal%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20narrated%20everything%20to%20him%2C%20I%20broke%20down.%20He%20mentored%20and%20motivated%20me%20to%20use%20my%20personal%20tragedy%20to%20help%20others.%20I%20realised%20if%20a%20person%20like%20me%20who%20had%20some%20knowledge%20of%20cybersecurity%20could%20become%20a%20victim%2C%20then%20what%20about%20young%20school%20and%20college-going%20students%3F%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1705499518.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Murthy%20says%20that%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20then-commissioner%20of%20police%20V%20C%20Sajjanar%20gave%20him%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1705499518.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1705499518-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the